_sText:
New map from FFMT Dieu which is the first map of a new concept : bt_ : battle titans !

In this map, there is one alone terrorist maximum ! But the CTs can be 32 ! The terrorist has a M3, a Deagle, a knife, and a suit... And the terrorist ,for every player CT, has 170HP suplementary, and the CTs can buy weapons, and they have to begin $10.000...

This is an original concept which is a little as a zombie mod, but without the scripts ^^...

/!\ You must have Mani Admin Plugin for the commands (ma_give, and so on...)

ENJOY !

PS : I'm sorry my english is not perfect... ^^
